content: 🎯 TRADING STRATEGY FIXES COMPLETE: Applied brutal audit corrections to TSLA ATR Pullback strategy. STRATEGY IMPROVEMENTS: Realistic commission (2bps), slippage (1 tick), proper session filtering, volatility gating. FILE CREATED: src/trading_robot/strategies/TSLA_ATR_Pullback_v2.pine (131 lines).
